# Release v0.2.0 — File Changes

## 1. Version Bump

#### [MODIFY] [Cargo.toml](file:///d:/own/saas/mediagit-core/Cargo.toml)
- Line 21: `version = "0.1.0"` → `"0.2.0"`
- Propagates to all 14 crates (all use `version.workspace = true`)

## 2. CHANGELOG

#### [MODIFY] [CHANGELOG.md](file:///d:/own/saas/mediagit-core/CHANGELOG.md)
- Promote `[Unreleased]` → `[0.2.0] - 2026-03-05`
- Update comparison links

## 3. Release Workflow Fixes

#### [MODIFY] [release.yml](file:///d:/own/saas/mediagit-core/.github/workflows/release.yml)

Two fixes:

**a) macOS Intel runner** (line 82):
`macos-13` → `macos-15-intel`

> [!IMPORTANT]
> `macos-13` was retired Dec 2025. `macos-14`/`macos-15` are Apple Silicon — **they cannot build x86_64 natively**. The correct label is `macos-15-intel` (Intel, available until Aug 2027).

**b) GHCR permission** (line 3-6):
Add `packages: write` — required for Docker push to `ghcr.io`

## User Setup (Not File Changes)

> [!WARNING]
> Before pushing tag, set `CARGO_REGISTRY_TOKEN` secret in GitHub repo settings (from crates.io/settings/tokens)
